headline: Assessing KeyCorp (KEY) Valuation After Recent Share Price Pullback And Longer Term Gains
summary: KeyCorp overview and recent share performance KeyCorp (KEY) has drawn investor attention after recent share price moves, with the stock showing a mix of short term pullback over the past week and gains over the past month and past 3 months. Over the past day, the share price return was about 0.3% lower, while the past week shows a decline of roughly 6.5%. In contrast, the stock is up around 3.6% over the past month and about 23.2% over the past 3 months, with a total return of roughly 28.4%...
